name: Community Pom
overview: Community Pom is a Role-Playing game, developed and published by Fill-In Cafe, which was released in Japan in 1997. Community Pom sports seven dungeons of major plot importance, six more that are much smaller and important only for the loot, and one secret dungeon that boasts some of the toughest enemies in the game (like evil kewpie dolls slinging razor yoyos).
